<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : gair3528_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testează modificarea unui produs</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28471"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P233-44: ModificareProdusTestcase-1-ECP&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">gair3528</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se modifica un produs cu un nume valid. Restul datelor sunt asumate a fi valide. Se verifica daca produsul a fost modificat cu succes.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>&nbsp;- nume string si nume != null si nume != &quot;&quot;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.ProductServiceECPTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.ProductServiceECPTest#testUpdateProduct_ECP_Valid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">gair3528_F01:  ModificareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
